  "engines": [
    "Obrix"
  ],
  "description": "The Berlin School sound made from modular bricks. driftRate 0.009 and driftDepth 0.8 with journeyMode=1.0 — the Journey Paradox fulfilled: generative ambient that writes its own score. Two Triangle sources, detuned 3.5 semitones for natural beating. Poly 4 so voices drift against each other. Coprime LFOs at 0.067 and 0.11 Hz modulate LP cutoffs on two different processors — the filtering landscape shifts over 60-second cycles. Hold a chord and wait: the reef architects itself.",
